    "plan_content": "The plan is complete and saved at `/Users/timpietrusky/.claude/plans/compressed-dancing-kazoo.md`. Here's a summary of what I found and planned:\n\n---\n\n## Plan Summary: PulseBoard Channel Plugin\n\n**7 new files** under `extensions/pulseboard/` — zero modifications to existing files.\n\n### Key Finding: `getChatChannelMeta(\"pulseboard\")` won't type-check\n\n`ChatChannelId` is a strict union of the 9 channels in `CHAT_CHANNEL_ORDER` (`src/channels/ids.ts`) — `\"pulseboard\"` is not among them. Since we can't modify that file, `meta` in `channel.ts` will be defined as an inline object literal matching the `ChannelMeta` shape, not via a `getChatChannelMeta()` call.\n\n### Files to create\n\n| File | Pattern from |\n|---|---|\n| `extensions/pulseboard/package.json` | `extensions/nostr/package.json` |\n| `extensions/pulseboard/openclaw.plugin.json` | `extensions/irc/openclaw.plugin.json` |\n| `extensions/pulseboard/src/types.ts` | New: 3 interfaces (`PulseBoardAccount`, `PulseBoardConfig`, `PulseBoardMessage`) |\n| `extensions/pulseboard/src/runtime.ts` | `extensions/nostr/src/runtime.ts` |\n| `extensions/pulseboard/src/channel.ts` | `extensions/irc/src/channel.ts` (simplified) |\n| `extensions/pulseboard/index.ts` | `extensions/irc/index.ts` |\n| `extensions/pulseboard/setup-entry.ts` | `extensions/irc/setup-entry.ts` |\n\n### Notable implementation details for `channel.ts`\n- `ChannelConfigAdapter` requires both `listAccountIds` and `resolveAccount` (stubs returning empty/default)\n- `ChannelOutboundAdapter` is a **flat** object — `deliveryMode`, `textChunkLimit`, and `sendText` are all top-level (not nested under `base`/`attachedResults`)\n- `gateway.startAccount` logs the connection and returns `{ stop: () => {} }`\n- `index.ts` needs the `as ChannelPlugin` type cast (same as IRC and Telegram)\n\n### Verification\n`git diff --name-only` (only new files), `pnpm tsgo`, `pnpm check`",
